<br>
Yes I want something fair for everyone, this new proposal I dont feel is fair. Especially to smaller guilds who have no difficulty clearing Planes on their own. Under this new proposal, any guild or alliance with less then 40 members loses their right to post. And to top it off even if you have a lot of members, you still have a Big Brother guild to back you up. Sorry but if I have 50+ guild/alliance members on the plane with me, I more then likely will not need a big brother guild, ever.<br>
<br>
In my first reply to this string I asked that the large guilds, medium guilds and small guilds all get together and come up with a plan they can support. This would have to happen in a chat room because in my honest opinion nothing can be decided here. We will never get one plan everyone gets all warm and fuzzy over but we can come up with something everyone supports. If a few guilds hate it and the rest like it then the rest of us enforce it. Thorfinn tried doing this already and the large guilds never showed up, if everyone wants to work it out, lets put some effort into getting someone there next time.<br>
<br>
A lot of people have great ideas on these boards, we could gather them all and put them into one that will probably work out just fine. Also, many of the problems with getting planes access will be gone in a few weeks so that has to be considered also.<br>
<br>
